title: Tucson DUI Attorney
name: Tucson DUI Attorney
description: We are experienced DUI attorneys in Tucson Arizona. We aggressively defend Tucson DUI charges both in court and at DMV hearings, by strategizing with clients to develop an effective defense. We want to know why the Tucson police stopped your car, how well you performed on the field sobriety tests, whether the officer completed a 15-minute observation period prior to the breath test, and if the machine had any history of malfunction.
